/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Phan-Huy-%C3%8Dch/Thu-ph%E1%BB%A5ng-qu%E1%BB%91c-tang-c%E1%BA%A3m-thu%E1%BA%ADt-k%E1%BB%B3-2/poem-TiPQXePndHWUNm9TEnzSUg">Thu phụng quốc tang cảm thuật kỳ 2 - 秋奉國喪感述其二</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Phan-Huy-%C3%8Dch/author-geNjG6kbAxWPLaqdF181sQ">Phan Huy Ích</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/H%E1%BB%93-L%E1%BB%87nh-N%C4%83ng/Ti%E1%BB%83u-nhi-thu%E1%BB%B3-%C4%91i%E1%BA%BFu/poem-FfnOgV00KakzA7tk5VxTwg">Tiểu nhi thuỳ điếu - 小兒垂釣</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/H%E1%BB%93-L%E1%BB%87nh-N%C4%83ng/author-NQboKNumscuMTrMsx-MrUg">Hồ Lệnh Năng</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C5%A9-Huy-T%E1%BA%A5n/Tri%E1%BB%81u-h%E1%BB%93i-h%E1%BB%89-ph%C3%BA/poem-4mIFtbpooOMqE0Nxb_Ltxw">Triều hồi hỉ phú - 朝回喜賦</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C5%A9-Huy-T%E1%BA%A5n/author-Ptt2M8z98OAIiQfyBrIxHw">Vũ Huy Tấn</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Dung/Xu%C3%A2n-du-h%E1%BB%93i-v%C4%83n-thi/poem-YFIj-vYYJTb3lrmUtTaN_g">Xuân du hồi văn thi - 春遊回文詩</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Dung/author-qXPPibIiYGXM8D15wPwoFg">Vương Dung</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
